	eattle location\, where clinical care meets community focused service. VMF
	H is known for delivering high quality\, patient centered healthcare while
	 investing deeply in prevention\, access\, and partnerships that strengthe
	n the neighborhoods they serve\, including West Seattle. In person network
	ing remains effective because face to face interaction improves trust\, cl
	arity\, and follow up\, a conclusion supported by Harvard Business Review 
	research comparing in person and virtual business relationships. This even
	ing offers space for thoughtful\, healthy conversation and relationship bu
